The module enables you to show product combinations as well as 'Add to Cart' button just within the product minitiature in the catalog. Both features increase the coversion rate.<br />

To change the text, the translation of 'Sold Out' and 'Save' labels, as well as 'Add to Cart' button:<br />
<ul>
<li>Open International / Translations</li>
<li>Select 'Theme Translations' type for the 'Modify Translations' block</li>
<li>Finally, select the theme and language you want to modify.</li>
</ul>
